CREATE_ACROSTIC_TO_SHARE: Hangaia he rerenga korero acrostic hei tiri.
HELP1: Ko te 'Acrostics Maker' he taputapu hei awhina i te hanga raupapa kupu, rerenga korero ranei hei maumahara i tetahi kupu ma ona reta.
HELP10: Tena koa kia koa, horahia te kupu pai i awhina a 'Acrostics Maker' ki a koe ki te maumahara ki nga ingoa motuhake o to oranga.
HELP2: Hei tauira, hei maumahara ki te {spcNm}, he mammmal rite racoon-4-waewae no Madagascar, ka taea e koe te whakamahi i tenei acrostic:
HELP3: Kua whakarārangihia ngā kupu ki ngā tīwae i raro i ia pū o te kupu acrostic.
HELP4: Ka whakaraupapahia e nga kupu ahua kua tohua me nga tuhinga papakupu kua whakarārangihia ki raro i ia kupu kupu mo ia reta.
HELP5: Ka tohua nga tuhinga papakupu mena kei roto i te whakamaramatanga te kupu ahua.
HELP7: Tīpakohia kia kotahi kupu i ia tīwae mō ia pū
HELP8: Whakatikahia te kupu kei runga ake ina hiahiatia.
HELP9: Patohia te 'Copy Acrostic' ki runga ki te kape i to acrostic.
